cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with multi-target tracking in videos. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as tracking is a common task in robotics. The paper also introduces a dynamic version of the successive shortest-path algorithm, which is a machine learning algorithm, making it likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper addresses the optimal solution to the data association problem, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography (cs.CR).
